{"name":"Dragon Guard Combo Jet","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/rifle-brown.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Fl8oVaAyEIeerrEF"}},"system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p>This weapon fires explosive-tipped miniature rocket shells that burst into balls of fire on impact. Its intimidation value is not to be underestimated. The combo version comes with an integrated flamethrower.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Explosive Ammunition: </strong>This weapon's damage is increased by 4 after damage reduction from armor is calculated.</p>\n<p><strong>Jetgun: </strong>This weapon gains <strong>+2 AP </strong>at ranges over half range.</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords: </strong>Assault, Long-Range</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","bulk":2.5,"charge":0,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":true,"hands":1,"damageType":"Explosive","damage":"2d10+12","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":6,"maxHits":3,"range":15,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401111777,"modifiedTime":1763401111777,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"3qoWVf5LNvyugLTW"}
{"name":"Flashbang Grenade W","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-glow-yellow.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.qAIUQsemUaRiQf87"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<h3 id=\"docs-internal-guid-06b60271-7fff-e120-8fcb-50a4ae85eff9\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 16pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Arial; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Flashbang Grenade</span></h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tier 2</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Difficulty 3; Dodge DC 5</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Range: Burst 2 within 10</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Hit: Targets are blinded and dazed (save ends both).</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Miss: Targets are dazed for 1 round.</span></p>","bulk":0,"charge":0,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"0","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":1,"range":null,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":1,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401118741,"modifiedTime":1763401118741,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"71iUNZKTklfahFyw"}
{"name":"Alchymic Double Barrel","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-double-barrel.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SN0M66AjHQvjwpk8"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>This shotgun fires volleys of corrosive particles at its hapless targets.<br /><br />This weapon fires in a seven square long, 25 degree wide cone. It requires 2 AP to fire. All targets must dodge (D 6).</p>\n<p><strong>On hit: </strong>D 4 stamina save; on fail: shred 3 armor, also 5 ongoing chemical damage (save ends).</p>","bulk":2,"charge":0,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Impact","damage":"d6+15","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":5,"maxHits":1,"range":7,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401108039,"modifiedTime":1763401108039,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"8hc9Oq3b3B0Ty7JK"}
{"name":"Perfector Mk IV Suppressed Rifle","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.c47V67dSmJR67LqR"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>This unassuming gun has an incredibly responsive, almost noiseless mechanism <br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" /><br /></p>\n<h3>Effects:</h3>\n<p>This weapon comes with a highly effective suppressor. You gain 2 automatic successes when rolling infiltration to remain undetected after firing this weapon.</p>","bulk":1,"charge":0,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Impact","damage":"1d6+15","ap":3,"hitBonus":3,"increment":5,"maxHits":1,"range":24,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"Sniper Rifle","targetArmor":"Armor"},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401144691,"modifiedTime":1763401144691,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"A34myzpgfRHAOxw5"}
{"name":"Nightpiercer","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-topbarrel.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.hvtqqa6qMR3aZfCq"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>The WN-1091 \"Nightpiercer\" model sniper rifle was issued by the Wayfinders to operatives and secret agents in need of long-range killing power. While it lacks the sheer penetrating capability of larger-caliber rifles, its relatively compact size makes it easy to conceal and set up in a position. The sights on this model of rifle were designed specially for use in poorly illuminated conditions, making this gun ideal for night-time ambush.</p>\n<h3>Effects:</h3>\n<p>Attacks made using a Nightpiercer ignore penalties for shooting in low light.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":0,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Piercing","damage":"1d3+11","ap":2,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":1,"range":20,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"successesPerHit":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401138442,"modifiedTime":1763401138442,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"AZwzs5f2GEs1zWF4"}
{"name":"Jet Black Pistol","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-brass.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.yN4tZXiFM8raovzJ"}},"system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p>This finely-crafted jet pistol not only looks impressive with its beautiful ebony sheen and the shine of the golden decorations on it, but the low-recoil explosive shells it fires also produce quite gruesome effects on soft targets.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Explosive Ammunition: </strong>This weapon's damage is increased by 4 after damage reduction from armor is calculated.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Jetgun: </strong>This weapon gains <strong>+2 AP </strong>at ranges over half range.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords: </strong>Assault, Long-Range, Sidearm</p>","bulk":1,"charge":0,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Explosive","damage":"1d8+4","ap":0,"hitBonus":2,"increment":0,"maxHits":4,"range":16,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401127087,"modifiedTime":1763401127087,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"BM5EqA4VNuA3G23v"}
{"name":"Heat Knife","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-double-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.s6Tme3aqYN2bIb0E"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This dagger contains a magic device that creates incredible heat around the blade when the user pushes a button on the hilt, allowing it to melt through most metals and set fire to flammable things. The magical nature of this contraption minimizes heat transfer to the blade itself, but prolonged use of this feature will eventually cause damage.</p>","bulk":0.5,"charge":0.5,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Fire","damage":"1d3+6","ap":3,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":4,"successesPerHit":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401092461,"modifiedTime":1763401092461,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"I1m81QXv7ufkcDnd"}
{"name":"Lantern Autopulse Rifle","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/scifigun.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9UHqiKmjLDoCo6vt"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This Order of the Lantern weapon fires focused blasts of force that penetrate conventional armor and cause severe blunt trauma in organic targets. While ineffective against military-grade energy protection, it is extremely useful in crowd control and counterinsurgency applications.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords: </strong>Rapid Fire, Assault</p>","bulk":1,"charge":0,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Force","damage":"1d8+5","ap":0,"hitBonus":2,"increment":0,"maxHits":4,"range":16,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"Crushing","targetArmor":"Magic Armor"},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401129201,"modifiedTime":1763401129201,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"JLJewUtQD3TlQ3DO"}
