{"name":"Construct Chaingun","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/gun-minigun-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.kub9w7gukRZX3nY7"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>The bane of light infantry, this construct-mounted weapon fires large-caliber shells at incredibly high rates.</p>\n<p><strong>Effects:</strong></p>\n<p>Gain +3 on your marksmanship rolls when you make a full attack with this weapon, due to its high rate of fire.</p>","bulk":3,"charge":0,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Piercing","damage":"1d8+8","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":3,"range":10,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"successesPerHit":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401109823,"modifiedTime":1763401109823,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"ctxtLTI0xf8VFj8j"}
{"name":"Silent Killer","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SMKCVKUH6H7adsui"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>The model WN-7404 \"Silent Killer\" suppressed sniper rifle was the favored assassination weapon of the Wayfinders. While comparatively short-ranged, the exceptional efficacy of the suppressor system ensured that a well-concealed assassin would remain undetected for long enough to make their escape.</p>\n<h3>Effects:</h3>\n<p>This weapon comes with a highly effective suppressor. You gain 2 automatic successes when rolling infiltration to remain undetected after firing this weapon.</p>","bulk":1,"charge":0,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Piercing","damage":"1d3+8","ap":2,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":1,"range":15,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"successesPerHit":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401148534,"modifiedTime":1763401148534,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"e4MNXXoLIUw7CoPD"}
{"name":"Construct Power Sword","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-broad-serrated-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.AJISCFfBocq6rFzD"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"","bulk":2,"charge":1,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Rending","damage":"15+d4","ap":4,"hitBonus":1,"increment":8,"maxHits":3,"quantity":null,"subType":"Sword","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401084229,"modifiedTime":1763401084229,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"gQj6NYWCAwd7E8Pb"}
{"name":"Lantern Jetgun","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-brass.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.jIqlLQ5QJOvF40nS"}},"system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p>This finely-crafted jet pistol not only looks impressive with its beautiful ebony sheen and the shine of the golden decorations on it, but the low-recoil explosive shells it fires also produce quite gruesome effects on soft targets.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Explosive Ammunition: </strong>This weapon's damage is increased by 4 after damage reduction from armor is calculated.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Jetgun: </strong>This weapon gains <strong>+2 AP </strong>at ranges over half range.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords: </strong>Assault, Long-Range, Sidearm</p>","bulk":1,"charge":0,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Explosive","damage":"1d12+7","ap":0,"hitBonus":2,"increment":8,"maxHits":4,"range":16,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401131116,"modifiedTime":1763401131116,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"gno1e3nhAs7wtNUt"}
{"name":"Spirit Bomb W","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/creatures/magical/spirit-mischief-fire-ice-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Pcd3hxtD5yBJDrp8"}},"system":{"tier":0,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-2c845f34-7fff-950d-2a8a-982260fb69ce\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tier 2</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Difficulty 4, Dodge DC 6</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Range: Burst 2 within 10</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Hit: 9+D8 Psychic damage; undead creatures take D8 additional damage. Corpses within range cannot be reanimated or revived for 2d3 rounds.</span></p>","bulk":0,"charge":0,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Psychic","damage":"9+d8","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":1,"range":null,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":1,"subType":"Grenade","targetArmor":"MA"},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401150939,"modifiedTime":1763401150939,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"h2F4nglfG9d5LYef"}
{"name":"Argent Disruptor","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/wands/wand-carved-stone-shard.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.gRXAxCfWMuehUS2D"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>This silvered power club brutally tears apart whatever material it touches. The surface ablation produced by the action of the power field leaves traces of the weapon's silver coating in every wound.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords: </strong>Silvered</p>","bulk":1.5,"charge":1,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Energy","damage":"1d8+9","ap":4,"hitBonus":4,"increment":0,"maxHits":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401076969,"modifiedTime":1763401076969,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"hVS553KqX8jkYbbZ"}
{"name":"Gathering Cloud Blade","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/greatsword-crossguard-engraved-green.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3R8RZbENtHDbGFbs"}},"system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p>This engraved blade crackles with electricity,</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>On hit: target must make a difficulty 5 stamina check; on failure it is dazed and takes 5 ongoing electric damage (save ends both).</p>","bulk":2,"charge":2,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"2d8+11","ap":4,"hitBonus":3,"increment":9,"maxHits":3,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401090157,"modifiedTime":1763401090157,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"o0gupzKlx9hHAEO7"}
