{"name":"Lantern Impulse Gauntlet","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/fist/fist-knuckles-brass.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.mVrEsvkhn17epwmK"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This lightweight projector gauntlet is commonly issued as a self-defence weapon to Lantern troops. It significantly augments the wearers' strength in a fist fight, enabling them to disengage effectively and end the threat with their service weapon.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords:</strong> Sidearm</p>","bulk":0.25,"charge":0,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Crushing","damage":"1d6+4","ap":2,"hitBonus":2,"increment":0,"maxHits":2},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401097858,"modifiedTime":1763401097858,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"p5qarm9O2nvDT8M0"}
{"name":"Acid Grenade W","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/magic/acid/projectile-smoke-glowing.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xYXfFfL34JLIwzU1"}},"system":{"tier":0,"name":"","description":"<h3 id=\"docs-internal-guid-d6ff23ec-7fff-a2fa-8b40-ab103ab96c00\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 16pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Arial; color: #434343; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Acid Grenade</span></h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tier 2</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Difficulty 3; Dodge DC 5</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Range: Burst 1 within 10</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Damage: 4+D10 Chemical, Shred 2</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Hit: Ongoing Chemical damage and Shred 2 per round (save ends both).</span></p>","bulk":0,"charge":0,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Chemical","damage":"4+d10","ap":2,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":1,"range":null,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":1,"subType":"Grenade","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401106035,"modifiedTime":1763401106035,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"q7axSnPkFhx2yckt"}
{"name":"Argent Keyblade","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-runed-glowing.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7zVkT91KmnLy846N"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>This surprisingly light two-handed sword uses force projector technology to enhance armor penetration. It is spellbound to increase effectiveness against undead creatures, and it has an ablative outer coating of silver that remains in the wounds caused by it.</p>\n<p><strong>Undeadbane:</strong> This sword inflicts 1d6 additional damage against undead creatures.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords: </strong>Sidearm, Silvered</p>","bulk":0.5,"charge":2,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Rending","damage":"9+2D8","ap":3,"hitBonus":2,"increment":5,"maxHits":2,"quantity":null,"subType":"Heavy","targetArmor":"Armor"},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401078677,"modifiedTime":1763401078677,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"uZeMLviiwiVrf7Xn"}
{"name":"Power Field Parry Dagger","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-blue.webp","system":{"tier":4,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 4 Dagger &bull; Powered</strong></p>\n<p>This dagger grants a +4 equipment bonus to parry checks.</p>","bulk":1,"charge":1,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"1d10+6","ap":12,"hitBonus":0,"increment":11,"maxHits":1,"quantity":1,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.XPxChNAdjLHWeNUk"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769894698619,"modifiedTime":1774473426404,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"wxOkyG2Hh107AykZ"}
{"name":"Kazykly","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-flared-silver-pink.webp","system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 6 Legendary Spear &bull; Blood, Shadow, Two-handed, Reach</strong></p>\n<p><em>Kazykly&nbsp;</em>is a&nbsp;<em>+2 Cursebringer Bloodthirst Lance</em>. It has the following traits:</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodthirst:&nbsp;</strong>The weapon hungers for the blood of its foes. If&nbsp;<em>Kazykly </em>successfully deals damage to a living target, the wielder gains a +2 bonus to the next attack with the weapon.</p>\n<p><strong>Cursebringer: </strong>The weapon brings doom to anything it strikes. If&nbsp;<em>Kazykly&nbsp;</em>successfully deals damage to a target, the target must make a D7 Potential save. On failure, it takes a -2 curse penalty to all of its rolls (save ends).</p>\n<p><strong>Reach:&nbsp;</strong>This weapon has a range of 3, but it cannot strike directly adjacent targets.</p>\n<p><strong>The Lord Impaler:&nbsp;</strong><em>Kazykly</em> grans its wielder the <em>Forest of Corpses&nbsp;</em>unique power.</p>","bulk":3,"charge":3,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"piercing","damage":"2d12+29","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":18,"maxHits":4,"quantity":null,"subType":"Lance","targetArmor":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Htd18cm7Cv6QUvUj"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767464172142,"modifiedTime":1774473431053,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"8DEpNQXOKXBciWdc"}
{"name":"Hoarfrost","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/skills/melee/weapons-crossed-swords-teal.webp","system":{"tier":5,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 5 Medium Sword &bull; Cold</strong></p>\n<p><em>Hoarfrost</em> is a&nbsp;<em>+2 Masterwork Rimebound Longsword</em>. It has the following traits:</p>\n<p><strong>Rimebound Blade</strong>&nbsp;<em>Hoarfrost</em> deals an additional 1D12+7 Cold damage on hit, reduced by ward (but not armor).</p>\n<p><strong>Unmelting Edge</strong> Attacks with this weapon gain a +2 Equipment bonus to their accuracy.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":2,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"1d12+7","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":14,"maxHits":1,"quantity":null,"subType":"sword","targetArmor":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Q91ix96d5K2Z2fE4"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1768689796153,"modifiedTime":1774473433198,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"JNaQF99RLUc5cj8m"}
{"name":"Moonlight Shortsword","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/shortsword-guard-silver.webp","system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Masterwork Shortsword, Tier 6 &bull; Moonlight</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Moontouched:<em>&nbsp;</em></strong>A target hit by this sword is surrounded by a halo of moonlight that makes it easier to hit. Any attacks against a afflicted by this power gain a +2 bonus until the end of the wielder's next turn; additionally, it cancels the effects of invisibility for this duration.</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodthirst:&nbsp;</strong>The weapon hungers for the blood of its foes. If&nbsp;<em>Silence </em>successfully deals damage to a living target, the wielder gains a +2 bonus to the next attack with the weapon.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":2,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"slashing","damage":"2d8+18","ap":9,"hitBonus":0,"increment":16,"maxHits":1,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Io9YnSS7ExpEWvXP"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1769894709006,"modifiedTime":1774473441767,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"qEB6DBf2vbfWBDZD"}
{"name":"Moonlight Railgun","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/rifle-fluted.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ShsGnv3f939Jq3fF"}},"system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Masterwork Sniper Rifle, Tier 6 &bull; Blood, Moonlight</strong></p>\n<p><strong>The Moonlight Railgun </strong>is a <em>+1 Moontouched Bloodthirst Sniper Rifle. </em>It has the following powers:</p>\n<p><strong>Moontouched:</strong><em>&nbsp;</em>A target hit by a shot from&nbsp;<em>Silence&nbsp;</em>is surrounded by a halo of moonlight that makes it easier to hit. Any attacks against a afflicted by this power gain a +2 bonus until the end of the wielder's next turn; additionally, it cancels the effects of invisibility for this duration.</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodthirst:&nbsp;</strong>The weapon hungers for the blood of its foes. If&nbsp;<em>Silence </em>successfully deals damage to a living target, the wielder gains a +2 bonus to the next attack with the weapon.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":1,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Piercing","damage":"2d12+14","ap":28,"hitBonus":0,"increment":18,"maxHits":1,"range":15,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"successesPerHit":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"Sniper Rifle","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767463333704,"modifiedTime":1774473452723,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"xqyiwZdwxXhkNqKm"}
{"name":"Silence","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-topbarrel.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9aCPq8VhKO8LXA7g"}},"system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Legendary Sniper Rifle, Tier 6 &bull; Blood, Moonlight</strong></p>\n<p><em>Palai azahhassa kazna yič ivi&scaron;nyawāng uraha ūr <strong>wī&scaron;&scaron;amp</strong> ivultwa.<br>On the field where bloody battle had raged, there reigned a great&nbsp;</em><strong><em>silence</em></strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Silence&nbsp;</strong>is a&nbsp;<em>Legendary </em><em>+2 Moontouched Bloodthirst Sniper Rifle.&nbsp;</em>It has the following powers:</p>\n<p><strong>Moontouched:</strong><em>&nbsp;</em>A target hit by a shot from&nbsp;<em>Silence&nbsp;</em>is surrounded by a halo of moonlight that makes it easier to hit. Any attacks against a afflicted by this power gain a +2 bonus until the end of the wielder's next turn; additionally, it cancels the effects of invisibility for this duration.</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodthirst:&nbsp;</strong>The weapon hungers for the blood of its foes. If&nbsp;<em>Silence </em>successfully deals damage to a living target, the wielder gains a +2 bonus to the next attack with the weapon.</p>\n<p><strong>Piercing Silence:&nbsp;</strong>The legendary power of&nbsp;<em>Silence.&nbsp;</em>Shots from this weapon are magically silenced and cannot be detected by auditory means outside of a radius of 5 meters from the weapon itself. Additionally, a target struck by&nbsp;<em>Silence&nbsp;</em>must make a D6 Potential check or be&nbsp;<em>silenced&nbsp;</em>(save ends). A target killed by a shot from&nbsp;<em>Silence&nbsp;</em>fails this check automatically.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":4,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Piercing","damage":"2d6+35","ap":5,"hitBonus":0,"increment":18,"maxHits":1,"range":15,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"successesPerHit":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"Sniper Rifle","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767463333704,"modifiedTime":1774473456600,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"ZsZfDKsALIsjvM3a"}
{"name":"Silence","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-topbarrel.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9aCPq8VhKO8LXA7g"}},"system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Legendary Sniper Rifle, Tier 6</strong></p>\n<p><em>Palai azahhassa kazna yič ivi&scaron;nyawāng uraha ūr <strong>wī&scaron;&scaron;amp</strong> ivultwa.<br>On the field where bloody battle had raged, there reigned a great&nbsp;</em><strong><em>silence</em></strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Silence&nbsp;</strong>is a&nbsp;<em>Legendary </em><em>+2 Sniper Rifle. </em>It has the following powers:</p>\n<p><strong>Piercing Silence:&nbsp;</strong>The legendary power of&nbsp;<em>Silence.&nbsp;</em>Shots from this weapon are magically silenced and cannot be detected by auditory means outside of a radius of 5 meters from the weapon itself. Additionally, a target struck by&nbsp;<em>Silence&nbsp;</em>must make a D6 Potential check or be&nbsp;<em>silenced&nbsp;</em>(save ends). A target killed by a shot from&nbsp;<em>Silence&nbsp;</em>fails this check automatically.</p>\n<p><strong>Silence&nbsp;</strong>can take up to two enchantments.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":4,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Piercing","damage":"2d6+35","ap":5,"hitBonus":0,"increment":18,"maxHits":1,"range":15,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"successesPerHit":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"Sniper Rifle","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767463333704,"modifiedTime":1774473528374,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"ZsZfDKsALIsjvM3a"}
{"name":"Void Blade","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/skills/melee/hand-grip-sword-white-brown.webp","system":{"tier":5,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Tier 5 Legendary Katana &bull; Void</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Nowhere Edge:</strong> The wielder of this Katana gains access to the <em>Wounds from Nowhere&nbsp;</em>legendary power.</p>\n<p><strong>Spacerender&nbsp;</strong>The&nbsp;<em>Void Blade&nbsp;</em>has a reach of 2.</p>\n<p><strong>Soul Drain&nbsp;</strong>The&nbsp;<em>Void Blade&nbsp;</em>forces a target hit by it to make a D6 Potential save. On failure, the target loses 1 EP and 1D10+15 Focus.</p>","bulk":1,"charge":2,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"crushing","damage":"1d10+15","ap":15,"hitBonus":0,"increment":15,"maxHits":2,"quantity":null,"subType":"Sword","targetArmor":""},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.jbAsj8CMb1sVjj0c"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1770501093597,"modifiedTime":1774473712365,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"7RNAfasSmhv6DA8y"}
