{"name":"Nightpiercer","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-topbarrel.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.hvtqqa6qMR3aZfCq"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>The WN-1091 \"Nightpiercer\" model sniper rifle was issued by the Wayfinders to operatives and secret agents in need of long-range killing power. While it lacks the sheer penetrating capability of larger-caliber rifles, its relatively compact size makes it easy to conceal and set up in a position. The sights on this model of rifle were designed specially for use in poorly illuminated conditions, making this gun ideal for night-time ambush.</p>\n<h3>Effects:</h3>\n<p>Attacks made using a Nightpiercer ignore penalties for shooting in low light.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":0,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Piercing","damage":"1d3+11","ap":2,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":1,"range":20,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"successesPerHit":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401138442,"modifiedTime":1774473751849,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"AZwzs5f2GEs1zWF4"}
