{"name":"Lantern Impulse Gauntlet","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/fist/fist-knuckles-brass.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.mVrEsvkhn17epwmK"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This lightweight projector gauntlet is commonly issued as a self-defence weapon to Lantern troops. It significantly augments the wearers' strength in a fist fight, enabling them to disengage effectively and end the threat with their service weapon.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords:</strong> Sidearm</p>","bulk":0.25,"charge":0,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Crushing","damage":"1d6+4","ap":2,"hitBonus":2,"increment":0,"maxHits":2,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401097858,"modifiedTime":1774473775313,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"p5qarm9O2nvDT8M0"}
{"name":"Lantern Jetgun","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-brass.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.jIqlLQ5QJOvF40nS"}},"system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p>This finely-crafted jet pistol not only looks impressive with its beautiful ebony sheen and the shine of the golden decorations on it, but the low-recoil explosive shells it fires also produce quite gruesome effects on soft targets.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Explosive Ammunition: </strong>This weapon's damage is increased by 4 after damage reduction from armor is calculated.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Jetgun: </strong>This weapon gains <strong>+2 Pen </strong>at ranges over half range.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords: </strong>Assault, Long-Range, Sidearm</p>","bulk":1,"charge":0,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Explosive","damage":"1d12+7","ap":0,"hitBonus":2,"increment":8,"maxHits":4,"range":16,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401131116,"modifiedTime":1774473784485,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"gno1e3nhAs7wtNUt"}
{"name":"Lantern Autopulse Rifle","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/scifigun.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9UHqiKmjLDoCo6vt"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This Order of the Lantern weapon fires focused blasts of force that penetrate conventional armor and cause severe blunt trauma in organic targets. While ineffective against military-grade energy protection, it is extremely useful in crowd control and counterinsurgency applications.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords: </strong>Rapid Fire, Assault</p>","bulk":1,"charge":0,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Force","damage":"1d8+5","ap":0,"hitBonus":2,"increment":0,"maxHits":4,"range":16,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"Crushing","targetArmor":"Ward"},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401129201,"modifiedTime":1774473797942,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"JLJewUtQD3TlQ3DO"}
{"name":"Lantern Autopulse Rifle","type":"rangedWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/scifigun.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9UHqiKmjLDoCo6vt"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This Order of the Lantern weapon fires focused blasts of force that penetrate conventional armor and cause severe blunt trauma in organic targets. While ineffective against military-grade energy protection, it is extremely useful in crowd control and counterinsurgency applications.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords: </strong>Rapid Fire, Assault</p>","bulk":1,"charge":0,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Force","damage":"1d8+5","ap":0,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":4,"range":16,"fireModeSingleShot":false,"fireModeSemiAuto":false,"fireModeSemiAutoRoS":0,"fireModeFullAuto":false,"fireModeFullAutoRoS":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"Crushing","targetArmor":"Ward"},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401129201,"modifiedTime":1774473800671,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"JLJewUtQD3TlQ3DO"}
{"name":"Heat Knife","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-double-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.s6Tme3aqYN2bIb0E"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This dagger contains a magic device that creates incredible heat around the blade when the user pushes a button on the hilt, allowing it to melt through most metals and set fire to flammable things. The magical nature of this contraption minimizes heat transfer to the blade itself, but prolonged use of this feature will eventually cause damage.</p>","bulk":0.5,"charge":0.5,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Fire","damage":"1d3+6","ap":3,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":4,"successesPerHit":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401092461,"modifiedTime":1774473823300,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"I1m81QXv7ufkcDnd"}
