{"name":"Construct Chainsword","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/sword-chainsword-steampunk.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.fCwB8nVzh2SGdT3P"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>A weapon suitable both for attacking heavily armored targets and breaking through light fortifications. The sharp teeth on this motorized weapon come to life with a distinctly loud buzz.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":0,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Slashing","damage":"1d12+6","ap":2,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":2,"successesPerHit":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401080701,"modifiedTime":1774473848347,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"Tjw7316NH9jJYMBc"}
{"name":"Argent Disruptor","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/wands/wand-carved-stone-shard.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.gRXAxCfWMuehUS2D"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>This silvered power club brutally tears apart whatever material it touches. The surface ablation produced by the action of the power field leaves traces of the weapon's silver coating in every wound.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Keywords: </strong>Silvered</p>","bulk":1.5,"charge":1,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Energy","damage":"1d8+9","ap":4,"hitBonus":4,"increment":0,"maxHits":3,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401076969,"modifiedTime":1774473853413,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"hVS553KqX8jkYbbZ"}
{"name":"Dragon Guard Longsword","type":"meleeWeapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-guard-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pO2EzpFQ0y3Anhjm"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This sturdy power sword is the standard-issue infantry weapon of the Dragon Guard's Fraternity of Iron. When swung, it leaves a shimmering trail of heat reminescent of a dragon's fiery breath.</p>","bulk":1,"charge":0,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"hands":1,"damageType":"Slashing","damage":"1d6+6","ap":3,"hitBonus":0,"increment":0,"maxHits":3,"successesPerHit":0,"quantity":null,"subType":"","targetArmor":""},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401082496,"modifiedTime":1774473866273,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"UezDOBw6NYPFGIpF"}
